sent.orig: These results suggested that fSpd,fSpm,ASCC-PAs,AISCC-Put and AISCC-Spd played important roles in soybean seed dehydration process.
sent.trans: 结果表明，fSpdf、Spm、ASCC-PAs、AISCC-Put和AISCC-Spd在大豆种子成熟脱水过程中可能起重要作用。

sent.orig: Spermine(Spm)and putrescine(Put)content were significantly higher than cadavarine(Cad)and spermidine(Spd)during rhizome development.
sent.trans: 精胺(Spm)和腐胺(Put)在膨大过程中含量高，尸胺(Cad)和亚精胺(Spd)含量较低。

sent.orig: Never put off the work till tomorrow what you can put off today.
sent.trans: 不要等明天交不上差再找借口，今天就要找好。
